ETHICAL USE ADDENDUM:

This software is intended for crisis detection and harm prevention in
conversational AI systems. It shall NOT be used for:

1. Surveillance of individuals without explicit informed consent
2. Discrimination in employment, insurance, or services
3. Coercion or manipulation of vulnerable populations
4. Any application that violates human rights or dignity

Users deploying this software in production systems MUST:
- Obtain appropriate IRB/ethics approval
- Implement informed consent mechanisms
- Maintain human oversight (human-in-the-loop)
- Conduct regular fairness audits
- Provide transparency reports on false positive/negative rates

By using this software, you agree to these ethical constraints.

